---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import TopNav from '../../components/TopNav.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../components/Sidebar.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';

import { getSidebarGroups } from '../../data/sidebar-config.ts';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');

const sidebarGroups = getSidebarGroups('systems');
---
<BaseLayout title="Game Systems | MITE:BE Wiki" description="MITE:BE game systems overview: nutrition, combat, survival, skills. Detailed guide to the mod's unique mechanics.">
  <Header />
  <TopNav currentPage="systems" />
  <div class="container">
    <Sidebar groups={sidebarGroups} />
    <main class="content">

<div id="sys-summary" style="margin-bottom:16px; font-size:.9em; color:var(--text2);"></div>
<script is:inline>
(function() {
  var pages = ['nutrition','combat','survival','skills'];
  var labels = { hu: 'fejezet befejezve', en: 'chapters completed', ru: 'глав завершено' };
  try {
    var done = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('mite-wiki-progress') || '[]');
    var count = pages.filter(function(p) { return done.includes(p); }).length;
    var el = document.getElementById('sys-summary');
    if (el && count > 0) {
      var lang = (localStorage.getItem('mite-wiki-lang') || 'hu');
      var label = labels[lang] || labels.hu;
      el.innerHTML = '<span style="color:#4caf50">✓ ' + count + '/4</span> ' + label;
    }
  } catch(e) {}
})();
</script>

<div data-lang="hu">
<h2>⚙ A MITE:BE Játékrendszerei</h2>
<p>A MITE:BE számos összetett rendszerrel bővíti ki a Minecraft alapmechanikáit. Ezek a rendszerek egymással kölcsönhatásban alakítják a túlélési tapasztalatot.</p>

<div class="hub-grid">
  <a href={`${base}/systems/nutrition/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--green)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">🍖</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Táplálkozás</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">Étrend egyensúly, tápanyagok, víz és hidratáció. Egyoldalú étkezés alultápláltságot okoz!</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
  <a href={`${base}/systems/combat/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--accent)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">⚔</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Harc</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">Páncélok, fegyverek, varázslat, távolsági harc íjjal és nyilakkal.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
  <a href={`${base}/systems/survival/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--copper)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">🎒</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Túlélés</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">Hátizsákok, hőmérséklet-kezelés, tudáskönyvek és egyéb túlélési mechanikák.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
  <a href={`${base}/systems/skills/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--gold)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">📜</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Képességek</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">11 szakma (kovácsmesterség, ácsmesterség, főzés stb.) és tudáskönyvek rendszere.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
</div>
</div>

<div data-lang="en">
<h2>⚙ MITE:BE Game Systems</h2>
<p>MITE:BE extends Minecraft's base mechanics with numerous complex systems. These systems interact with each other to shape the survival experience.</p>

<div class="hub-grid">
  <a href={`${base}/systems/nutrition/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--green)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">🍖</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Nutrition</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">Diet balance, nutrients, water and hydration. One-sided eating causes malnutrition!</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
  <a href={`${base}/systems/combat/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--accent)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">⚔</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Combat</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">Armor, weapons, enchanting, ranged combat with bows and arrows.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
  <a href={`${base}/systems/survival/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--copper)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">🎒</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Survival</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">Backpacks, temperature management, knowledge books, and other survival mechanics.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
  <a href={`${base}/systems/skills/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--gold)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">📜</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Skills</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">11 professions (blacksmithing, carpentry, cooking etc.) and the Knowledge Books system.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
</div>
</div>

<div data-lang="ru">
<h2>⚙ Игровые системы MITE:BE</h2>
<p>MITE:BE расширяет базовую механику Minecraft множеством сложных систем, которые взаимодействуют друг с другом и формируют опыт выживания.</p>

<div class="hub-grid">
  <a href={`${base}/systems/nutrition/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--green)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">🍖</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Питание</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">Баланс рациона, питательные вещества, вода и гидратация. Однобокое питание вызывает недоедание!</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
  <a href={`${base}/systems/combat/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--accent)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">⚔</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Бой</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">Броня, оружие, зачарование, дальний бой с луком и стрелами.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
  <a href={`${base}/systems/survival/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--copper)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">🎒</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Выживание</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">Рюкзаки, управление температурой, книги знаний и другие механики выживания.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
  <a href={`${base}/systems/skills/`} class="hub-card" style="--card-accent: var(--gold)">
    <div class="hub-card-icon">📜</div>
    <div class="hub-card-body">
      <div class="hub-card-title">Навыки</div>
      <div class="hub-card-desc">11 профессий (кузнечное дело, плотницкое дело, кулинария и др.) и система Книг знаний.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-card-arrow">→</div>
  </a>
</div>
</div>

    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
